item.description:
Open air picnic for members and friends. No formal presentation or agenda. Bring food and drinks for yourself or to share.
This is a weather dependent event, if rain is probable, we will reschedule.

Meet at intersection of South St and Bussey (inside park). Look for Free State Project Tshirt. I suggest entering via the South St gate instead of Forest Hills gate. Parking is available in the area but may be scarce. Closest T stop is Forest Hills (Orange line).

Note that mobile phone reception is weak there, so don't count on being able to use phone/internet for directions.

http://arboretum.harvard.edu/visit/directions/
